<dashboard>
  <label>Multi-Layer Groups</label>
  <row>
    <panel>
      <html>
      <p>
        The default behavior is to group like icons into the same layer group. Use the <code>layerGroup</code> field for granular control over layer grouping. To group all markers into a single layer, simply <code>| eval layerGroup="default" | table layerGroup</code>
      </p>
      <p>
        Toggle the visibility of each layer using the layer controls panel in the upper right corner of the map.
      </p>
    </html>
    </panel>
  </row>
